# jobs

Syntax:
-------
	jobs [-options] <jobspec>
	jobs -x [command] <args>

Description:
------------
	Lists the jobs according to <jobspec>. Without option, status of all active job is displayed.

Option:
-------
	-l		Lists process ID in addition to the normal information.
	-n		Lists only processes that have changed status since the last notification.
	-p		Lists process ID only.
	-r		Restricts output to running jobs.
	-s		Restricts output to stopped jobs.

